        <summary type="html">Last week, we wrapped up our second season of the Virtual Coffee (VC) Podcast with our Code and Community episode. As VC‚Äôs been growing over the last year, I‚Äôve been working on the Virtual Coffee model for communities, and Dan and I have spent a lot of time talking through navigating the challenges and creating a direction for our unique community with the support and care of the community.</summary>
      

      
      
